trashday.model

Class Schedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • trashday.model.Schedule
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class Schedule
extends Object
    Data structure for the weekly pickup schedule.

    The schedule is fundamentally a Map using pickup names (String) as keys to refer to a Set of pickup times (TimeOfWeek). It keeps a List of pickup names as a convenience to keep ordering.

    The class implements Jackson Model Versioning using the "@JsonVersionedModel" and ToCurrentSchedule class.

    Author:
    J. Todd Baldwin
    See Also:
    Jackson Module: Model Versioning
